                    </div>
                    <span>Yes, this seems to be an average year. 1999's edition was much better. In fact, I think the best story in the book was the introduction by Amy Tan! Doctorow's intro this year was pretty lame.<P>If you're looking for something more exciting, grab the Best New American Voices 2000.</span>
                  
              
